License and IP

The software is released under a BSD-2-Clause license.
The complete text of the license is in the file named "LICENSE"
on the top-level directory.

There is no copyright assignement, nor a CLA for participating
on this project.  Each contriburor maintains authorship of their code.

In case you want to contribute code by someone else,
please put it into a separate directory under the "3rd_party" tree.
